        </button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="result-section" aria-labelledby="investigation-result">
      <div class="retro-titlebar">
        <span>Investigation Complete</span>
        <span class="mini-window-controls" aria-hidden="true">
          <span>_</span>
          <span>□</span>
          <span>×</span>
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="result-body">
        <p class="eyebrow">Investigation result</p>
        <h2 id="investigation-result">Human review required</h2>
        <div class="result-story">
          <p>Pricing logic changed.</p>
          <p>Existing tests still passed.</p>
          <p>Coverage showed the new path wasn't exercised.</p>
